Title: [ANN] [ICO] Robomed Network - a new medical network managed by blockchain token
Body: CONGRESS OF THE UNITED STATES REFERS TO ROBOMED NETWORK AS AN EXAMPLE OF BLOCKCHAIN INNOVATION COMPANIES    Robomed Network is proud to appear in March 2018 United States Joint Economic Committee Report: https://www.congress.gov/1…/crpt/hrpt596/CRPT-115hrpt596.pdf  “Unlike many innovations that attempt to skirt laws or regulations and become associated with the underground, these new blockchain products attempt to comply with the current system and even work together with regulators. The new products range from coordinating payment (healthnexus), monitoring and rewarding patients for following clinical recommendations (RoboMed Network), tracking pharmaceuticals along the supply chain (MediLedger), and even identifying specific supply chain problems such as those associated with the opioid crisis (BlockMedx)” – states Chapter 9: Building A Secure Future, One Blockchain At A Time.

Body: Robomed Network token growth principle  We often receive questions about RBM token and its rate.  Here is the in detailed answer:    The difference between RBM token and many other cryptocurrencies with no reinforcement is the fact that RBM token is intimately connected with the real world. Robomed Network will be released on market with high demand (the medical service) and will be claimed inevitably. The higher will be the demand the higher will raise the RBM token price because the amount of tokens is limited.  The project’s ecosystem will be presented on May. Robomed Network will enter the market and will be launched in clinics in the second half of 2018. All clinics connected to Robomed Network are obligated to accept the RBM token as payment for any medical services. Thus, the price of RBM token will increase. Author: robomed
Title: [ANN] [ICO] Robomed Network - a new medical network managed by blockchain token
Body: Robomed Network token Use case 2: Medical data aggregation  We continue a series of use cases devoted to RBM token.    As the patient’s healing proceeds, the clinics that are connected to Robomed Network collect more and more information about his condition and therapy. Those data are stored by means of EHR (electronic health record).  The patient has the option to give access permission to medical organizations that can use them anonymously for pharmaceutical researches, targeted advertising, applications, services and more. In case the patient agrees, he will receive RBM tokens for his data.  Thus, the patient can both expand the medical database and get his own reward. Author: robomed
Title: [ANN] [ICO] Robomed Network - a new medical network managed by blockchain token
Body: “The project that can be core on non-government market”  “Colleagues from Robomed are experienced in building wildly successful project in non-government medicine in relation to clinics’ capacity and healthcare quality control methods”, — says Yury Krestinskiy, Robomed Network’s investor. Mr. Krestinskiy is the Director of SKOLKOVO Health Economics and Management Centre and owner of BIONIKA group. He started his first business in 1991 in the publishing industry and came to healthcare and pharmaceutical industry in 1992 as the head of one of the first wholesale companies in Russia. In 1993 Yury Krestinskiy founded weekly newspaper PharmVestnik, since that year a number of publishing, advertising, recruitment and analytical projects were initiated and implemented on its basis. These projects were brought together and exists until now as BIONIKA Group established under Yury Krestinskiy’s leadership. “Commitment to Robomed cryptocurrency is an indirect investment to the project that can be core on non-government market in Russia and other countries”, — states Mr. Krestinskiy. You can find more (in Russian) at https://lenta.ru/news/2017/10/25/tokeni_robmed/ Participate in Robomed Network ICO at https://robomed.io/

Author: robomed
Title: [ANN] [ICO] Robomed Network - a new medical network managed by blockchain token
Body: With the help of Robomed Mobile the patient can receive telemedicine consultations, appoint, postpone, or cancel their visits, choose whom to show their medical data and enter into smart contracts with medical organizations.  Robomed Web is the desktop version of Robomed Mobile, deployed for the convenience of the patient. It allows you to fully use all the benefits of the Robomed Network on any computer without the need to download any software. Also, Robomed Web is used to access the medical knowledge base and to conduct voting by the medical community and the patient community in determining or updating the value criteria of various health services and outcomes.

Author: robomed
Title: [ANN] [ICO] Robomed Network - a new medical network managed by blockchain token
Body: Hello itogo. Thus, for example, after the Robomed integration in one of the Russian multi-faceted medical clinics, the clinic’s profitability rate rose from 8% to 25% in a period of 6 months; the breakeven point was reached in two months; and the clinic’s sales turnover increased by 85% on year-to-year basis. Another example is a rehabilitation medical center, which showed a negative revenue growth of - 24%. After the RBM integration had been completed, the clinic’s profitability rate rose to 3% in six months, payback period was reached in two months.

Title: [ANN] [ICO] Robomed Network - a new medical network managed by blockchain token
Body: ROBOMED NETWORK TOKEN PRESALE IS NOW LAUNCHED  Robomed Network — a medical network designed to provide the most effective medical care, launches the presale of RBM tokens.    Robomed Network team consists of real professionals with rich experience in healthcare and innovative projects. Among them are: William Pecham – partner and investment director at Central Capital, and Jean-Elie Malkin – senior medical expert, ex-director of Global Alliance for Health and Social Compact (GAHSC).    The Robomed Network token presale will last starting from October 25 till November 14, 2017.  During the presale period, you have a unique chance to purchase RBM tokens with a 30% bonus!  Mankind will always be in need of medicine. Robomed Network tokens are a perfect investment to a perspective ever-evolving field.  More information on Robomed Network official website https://robomed.io/ru/token.php

Title: [ANN] [ICO] Robomed Network - a new medical network managed by blockchain token
Body: Robomed Network is a medical network managed by a blockchain token and designed to provide the most effective medical care.  The Robomed Network ecosystem connects healthcare service providers and patients based on a smart contract, the value criteria of which are the performance metrics of a specific medical service and patient satisfaction. This particular concept of a patient-oriented medical network, based on breakthrough technology, is new to the healthcare market.  The presale of Robomed tokens (RBM tokens) starts on October 25, 2017.  More details on www.robomed.io

Author: robomed
Title: [ANN] [ICO] Robomed Network - a new medical network managed by blockchain token
Body: BLOCKCHAIN CHANGES HEALTHCARE AND MEDICAL INSURANCE: PRESENTATION OF ROBOMED’S CO-FOUNDER AT ICO EVENT LONDON  On October 11, co-founder of Robomed project, CEO of Robomed Network Philipp Mironovich will speak at ICO event London. His presentation will focus on blockchain as a technology that will change medicine and insurance in the future.     Philipp Mironovich has been working in the field of medical services for seven years. As CEO of “Open Clinics” hospital network, he has won the Entrepreneur of the Year award. That is a prestigious international award for businessmen, founded by the British audit and consulting company EY (Ernst & Young).  In 2017, Philipp Mironovich has taken charge of the blockchain-based project Robomed, a new-generation medical insurer. The service offers to assess medical services and efficiency of treatment by the independent board of specialists; it relies on smart contracts.  In his presentation at ICO event London, Philipp Mironovich will dwell on how blockchain will change the future of medicine and medical insurance; how the technology will improve the quality of medical care and affordability of insurance services.  #robomed #robomednetwork #ico #blockchain #london

Title: [ANN] [ICO] Robomed Network - a new medical network managed by blockchain token
Body: Robomed Network considers the main Gibraltar principles  Gibraltar's Financial Services Commission has published a draft of its upcoming regulatory framework for firms offering blockchain services. Planned to come into effect from January 2018, the new rules will cover any commercial use of distributed ledger technology (DLT) as a means to store and transmit value.    Under the framework, DLT service providers will be granted a working license, providing they conform to some regulatory principles including honesty, integrity, the protection of customer assets and maintaining a high degree of cybersecurity.  Robomed Network Ltd is incorporated by Gibraltar Registrar of Companies and is proud to follow these principles. We remind that our presale starts on October 25, 2017.

Author: robomed
Title: [ANN] [ICO] Robomed Network - a new medical network managed by blockchain token
Body: Welcome to the official blog of Robomed Network – an innovative medical network!   Robomed Network issues its own tokens to support smart contract between healthcare providers and patients. RBM smart medical contract elevates service value by granting its owner full accomplishment of clinical guidelines for specific case by healthcare provider.  Robomed clinical guidelines are subject to constant improvement by the professional medical community, motivated for higher goals and bonuses by Robomed Network.                                                                          How will behave the RBM currency after entering the market? At the project development stage, until the demand for value-oriented medical services reaches the saturation limit, it is expected that monthly purchases of RBM will exceed RBM sales (exchange for other currencies). Thus, the price of RBM will grow over the long term, backed by the real product fulfilment with confirmed demand.    Why do you think people will buy RBM smart medical contacts? The answer is simple but perhaps may not be obvious to everyone. Healthcare is ought to be driven by a relentless focus on delivering outcomes that truly matter to patients and to society in a financially sustainable manner. But this is hard to do and hard to manage when the patient outcomes we should deliver are not clearly defined. Also, costs are increasing unsustainably with a significant fraction of healthcare spending wasted on low-value diagnostic procedures or treatments and on consequences of clinical errors. By eliminating inefficiencies, we can save approximately $1 trillion globally each year. Imagine the possibilities if we were to invest that capital in meaningful innovation or disease prevention. When it comes to out of pocket spending – nobody wants to waste his money or time. Our tool appears to be quite useful here.    How do you plan creating those much clinical guidelines and keep them up to date? The Robomed Network includes a tool for decentralized management of the criteria for the effectiveness of medical services. The active involvement of the professional medical community will be motivated by RBM payments for each vote, and the competence of holders of RBM Tokens admitted to professional medical voting will be checked throughout the authorization process. We believe that combined knowledge of professional medical community is there to help. We already have 2900 clinical guidelines digitalized.    What if some hospital doesn’t want to install your EHR? In case that the medical service provider does not want to work in the Robomed EHR, it can use any other EHR system and connect to the Robomed Network using the dedicated API under condition of the observation of the communication protocols according to the HL7 standard (or FHIR).    Who exactly is your customer? Our customer is an individual with a health problem with no insurance plan. He is willing to find the best solution for problem in a limited time and money. We provide this solution.    What if during RBM smart contact fulfillment an unusual result occurs? Although 90% of clinical cases are routine, such a thing can rarely happen. In that situation, this patient’s EMR with all his data except identity will become a subject to investigation by Robomed Network medical community with top priority.    How will you measure clinical guideline accomplishment by healthcare provider? Each clinical guideline consists of crucial milestones: completed services and medical data. Reference values of these milestones are the core of outcome measurement in Robomed EHR. Real time capture and reliability of block chain technology provides trustworthy information for such measurement.    What is a smart contract? Smart contracts are computer protocols intended to facilitate, verify, or enforce the negotiation or performance of a contract. Proponents of smart contracts claim that many kinds of contractual clauses may be made partially or fully self-executing, self-enforcing, or both. The aim of smart contracts is to provide security that is superior to traditional contract law and to reduce other transaction costs associated with contracting.   Please find more information about Robomed Network on the official website www.robomed.io and follow this thread for all the latest news and updates!  ----------------------------  Bounty campaign: https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=2765909  Information about Robomed Network is also available on: Social channels: Facebook: facebook.com/RobomedNetwork Twitter: twitter.com/Robomed_Network Telegram: t.me/RoboMed Telegram (Russian group): t.me/RoboMed_RUS Slack: robomedio.slack.com  Blog: Reddit: reddit.com/user/robomed Medium: medium.com/Robomed Golos: golos.io/@robomed Steemit: steemit.com/@robomed Bitcointalk: bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=2119569

Author: robomed
Title: [ANN] [ICO] Robomed Network - a new medical network managed by blockchain token
Body: Robomed Network unveils its features at Blockchain Meetup  The presentation of Robomed Network, a medical network managed by a blockchain token and designed to provide the most effective medical care, was held at IBCG’s Blockchain Meetup in Moscow on August 30, 2017.  Philipp Mironovich - the architect, visionary and investor of the Robomed Network, the founder of several projects in medicine, finalist of the EY 2015 "Entrepreneur of the Year" award and IT with 7 years of successful entrepreneurship in the medical market was speaking about the project that will completely change global medical industry.  Imagine that your fully protected health record is stored in blockchain so that you can grant access to it in any hospital connected to Robomed Network. Smart contracts grant the possibility to ensure best world practices in healing each particular disease. The special rankings system also allows providing the best services regarding both patients and consulting physicians.  It was also unveiled that one of the advisors of Robomed Network project became Thomas W. Feeley, M.D. - a Senior Fellow at the Harvard Business School.  «I really enjoyed reading through the whitepaper you sent and the PowerPoint presentation.  Your team has done an incredible job bringing together the latest in digital technology with blockchain technology. I have shared your information with Professor Porter and Dr. Zach Landman in San Francisco.  We have been writing a paper for 3 years on how health IT can support the value agenda.  We have known for some time that the US is interested in blockchain but the US market is strongly controlled by old systems using MUMPS and they refuse to change.  You can be disruptive» - comments Thomas W. Feeley.  The video of the event (in Russian) is available here: https://youtu.be/RBAC1S6w6yQ?t=555.  More information about Robomed Network can be found on the official website: www.robomed.io.  #robomed #robomednetwork #blockchain #token #medicine #health

Title: [ANN] [ICO] Robomed Network - a new medical network managed by blockchain token
Body: Getting more and more toke related with health, but up until now I've still got a little confused on how it will really work. How do it work, should the peoples just go and visit the health center or the health center will come to us?

Author: robomed
Title: [ANN] [ICO] Robomed Network - a new medical network managed by blockchain token
Body: Hello  itasannah!  This is how it works: in case the medical help is required the patient contacts Robomed Network. Based on each specific case and its database Robomed chooses a smart contarct for the patient and directs him or her to the clinic. When the points of smart contract are perfomed and the restoration to health comes the clinic receives its money according to the contract.

Author: robomed
